OL,3,CMan, 30, jailed for life for murdering
OL,4,Chis father
OL,6,FA man has received a life sentence for
OL,7,Fthe murder of his father in Bath
OL,8,Fearlier this year.
OL,10,FChristopher Monro, 30, will serve a
OL,11,Fminimum of 12 years in prison for
OL,12,Fkilling 73-year-old Peter Monro in
OL,13,FFebruary.
OL,15,FEmergency services were called at
OL,16,Faround noon on Tuesday 11 February,
OL,17,Fafter a carer found the father with
OL,18,Fknife wounds at his home in Kelston
OL,19,FView.
