OL,3,CMan, 30, jailed for life for murdering
OL,4,Chis father
OL,6,FResponding officers sadly confirmed Mr
OL,7,FMonro's death at the scene.
OL,9,FDuring the early stages of the
OL,10,Finvestigation, officers received
OL,11,Finformation Monro had been staying
OL,12,Fwith his father the weekend before,
OL,13,Fwith several people reporting having
OL,14,Fheard an argument two days before.
OL,16,FDetectives traced Christopher Monro's
OL,17,Fmovements, and he was subsequently
OL,18,Farrested at his home address in Osney
OL,19,FLane, Oxford, by Thames Valley Police
OL,20,Fthe following day.
