OL,3,CMan, 30, jailed for life for murdering
OL,4,Chis father
OL,6,FHe was subsequently charged with
OL,7,Fmurder, and he pleaded guilty at a
OL,8,Fhearing in August.
OL,10,FIn a statement, paying tribute to the
OL,11,Fman, Peter's family said their lives
OL,12,Fwill never be the same again.
OL,14,FThey said: "Peter Monro was an
OL,15,Fincredibly eccentric, funny,
OL,16,Fintelligent and unique man. He refused
OL,17,Fto be anything other than himself. A
OL,18,Fman of his own time. No one else's.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
