OL,3,CMan, 30, jailed for life for murdering
OL,4,Chis father
OL,6,F"His love of literature carried him
OL,7,Fthrough life and his sharp mind was
OL,8,Fimpossible to beat. We hope he is now
OL,9,Fwith the swallows."
OL,11,FThey also thanked loved ones for their
OL,12,Fsupport throughout, and the
OL,13,Fprofessionalism and empathy of
OL,14,Fspecialist family liaison police
OL,15,Fofficers.
