OL,3,CMan, 30, jailed for life for murdering
OL,4,Chis father
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Neil Meade, of the
OL,7,FMajor Crime Investigation Team, said:
OL,8,F"The past six months have been
OL,9,Fincredibly painful time for Peter's
OL,10,Ffamily and their touching tribute to
OL,11,Fhim is an indication of how loved he
OL,12,Fwas.
OL,14,F"This guilty plea comes following a
OL,15,Fcomprehensive police investigation and
OL,16,Fwe're grateful to Peter's family for
OL,17,Ftheir support while that process took
OL,18,Fplace, and the kind words they have
OL,19,Fsaid publicly.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
